I"S<h1 id="apt-widget">APT widget</h1>

<p>Widget which shows a list of APT packages to be updated:</p>

<p><img src="../awesome-wm-widgets/assets/img/widgets/screenshots/apt-widget/screenshot.gif" alt="screenshot" /></p>

<p>Features:</p>
<ul>
  <li>scrollable list !!! (thanks to this <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/awesomewm/comments/isx89x/scrolling_a_layout_fixed_flexed_layout_widget/">post</a> of reddit)</li>
  <li>update single package</li>
  <li>update multiple packages</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="installation">Installation</h2>

<p>Clone the repo under ~/.config/awesome/ folder, then in rc.lua add the following:</p>

<div class="language-lua highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">apt_widget</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"awesome-wm-widgets.apt-widget.apt-widget"</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="o">...</span>
<span class="n">s</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mytasklist</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="c1">-- Middle widget</span>
	<span class="p">{</span> <span class="c1">-- Right widgets</span>
    	<span class="n">layout</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wibox</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">layout</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">fixed</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">horizontal</span><span class="p">,</span>
		<span class="o">...</span>
		<span class="n">apt_widget</span><span class="p">(),</span>
		<span class="o">...</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

